The utilities and files in this directory are used to help make a workstation
or server a delivery node for "newprod" (more simply - allows users to connect
to a UNIX host with newprod to update their machines.)

The files and their uses are as follows:

Initial - tool that is used to initialize products and make them available for
	  newprod download

remote_newprod - utility that assists system administrators in updating remote
	  workstation/servers.
